How to build the toolchain which is used to compile the bootloader source
1, Please get Bootloader Toolchain from below link.
https://sourcery.mentor.com/GNUToolchain/package10389/public/mips-sde-elf/mips-2012.03-64-mips-sde-elf.src.tar.bz
2. build the toolchain
3. install the toolchain to /opt/


How to compile bootloader source
1. change directory to GPL_Uboot/
2. unzip and change directory to GPL_Uboot/Uboot
2, make 


How to get and use the final bootloader binary
1, change directory to GPL_Uboot/Uboot/mkbin/
2, ./bb
it will generate bootloader binary "R6260_boot.bin" (w/o ecc).
